"36:78:1" : {s: 36, a: 78, w: 1, r: "ضرب", t: "وَضَرَبَ", l: "ضَرَبَ", lc: 55, tl: "waḍaraba", lb: "উদাহরণ দেওয়া, আঘাত করা, আলাদা করা, ভ্রমন করা, রাগ প্রদর্শন করা",e: "And he sets forth", b: "উপমা পেশ করেছেন", i: "dan dia membuat", f: 4, rm: "to heal, strike, propound as an example, put forth a parable, go, make a journey, travel, mix, avoid, take away, put a cover, shut, mention/declare/state, propound, set forth, compare, liken, seek a way, march on, set, impose, prevent, fight, traffic with anyones property for a share in the profit, he made or caused to be or constituted, leave/forsake, take away thing (with an)."},
